The '''Namibia Water Corporation''' or '''NamWater''' is a [[parastatal]] in [[Namibia]]. It is wholly owned by the [[Agriculture ministry|Ministry of Agriculture]] of the Government of Namibia. The company employs over 600 people.<ref>[http://www.namwater.com.na/data/employees.html NamWater.com.na] Employee data</ref>

