'''Ship load''' is a [[United Kingdom]] unit of [[weight]] for [[coal]] equal to 949,760 [[pound (mass)|pounds]], 430803.889 [[kilogram|kg]], or 20 [[keel (unit)|keels]].<ref name=":0">{{Cite book|title = Encyclopaedia of Scientific Units, Weights and Measures|last = Cardarelli|first = François |publisher = Springer|year = 2003|isbn = 978-1-4471-1122-1|location = London|pages = 48}}</ref>

